Package: GenomicRearrangementPlot
Title: GenomicRearrangementPlot: an R package to visualize complex genome rearrangement profiles. 
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jose", "Espejo Valle-Inclan", , "jespejo@ebi.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4857-5984"))
